| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2936 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonransomware)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d66efcb9-5c35-5215-a645-c7f01943e895"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
